<div dir="ltr">Ralph,<div><br></div><div>Just to be clear - I can confirm only that &quot;make&quot; and &quot;make check&quot; pass.</div><div>Since it doesn&#39;t look like any ROMIO tests are included I cannot honestly say that I&#39;ve shown that it &quot;works&quot;.</div>
